pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `af76ca3` to `0511af6`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `af76ca3` to `0511af6`.
Commits
  • 0511af6 Update to Picnic 3.0.17 (#1280)
  • 42f36c2 Add option to all pytests to skip particular algorithms (#1282)
  • 84fde26 Fixup dilithium-avx2 valgrind test file (#1283)
  • 3cf9849 0.7.2-rc1
  • 91bfca9 Add library version retrieval function (#1273)
  • 33738d9 Update CODEOWNERS (#1274)
  • fe08f69 Fix FreeBSD runtime ARM CPU feature detection (#1267)
  • 1e47e14 Remove SIDH and SIKE (#1272)
  • See full diff in compare view
